<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Born Day Strategy</title>
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="data:image/png;base64,">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="data:image/png;base64,">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="Born Day Strategy">
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Big+Shoulders+Display:wght@700;800&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&family=Inter:wght@400;500&display=swap');

  :root{
    --paper: #FFFFFF;
    --ink: #000000;
    --line: #DEDAD0;
    --muted: #56514B;
    --amber: #B9862E;
    --green: #2E7D4F;
    --red: #B0392D;
    --ema9: #E0B400;
    --ema20: #C9622A;
    --ema50: #7A1F2B;
  }

  *{ box-sizing: border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }

  @page{
    size: auto;
    margin: 12mm;
  }

  @media print{
    html, body{
      background: #FFFFFF !important;
    }
    *{
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact !important;
      print-color-adjust: exact !important;
      color-adjust: exact !important;
    }
    body{
      padding: 0;
      display: flex !important;
      justify-content: center !important;
    }
    .card{
      max-width: 460px !important;
      width: 460px !important;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  html, body{ height: auto; min-height: 100%; }

  body{
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 16px;
  }

  .card{
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 460px;
    padding: 20px 30px 16px;
    position: relative;
  }

  h1{
    font-family: 'Big Shoulders Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    line-height: 0.9;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 4px 0 12px;
  }
  h1 em{
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ema50);
  }

  .emaline{
    width: 100%;
    height: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .row{
    display: flex;
    gap: 34px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .col{
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .col .grades,
  .col .tips{
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .label{
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .need-list{ list-style:none; }
  .need-list li{
    font-size: 12.5px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding-left: 12px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .need-list li::before{
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 7px;
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--ema50);
  }

  .bias{
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    line-height: 2;
  }
  .bias .up{ color: var(--green); font-weight: 600; }
  .bias .down{ color: var(--red); font-weight: 600; }
  .bias .note{
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .divider{
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    margin: 12px 0;
  }

  .ema-viz{
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .ema-state{ text-align: left; }
  .ema-state svg{ width: 100%; height: 20px; display:block; margin-bottom: 7px; }
  .ema-state .title{
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .ema-state .sub{
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 2px;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }
  .ema-state .verdict{
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .verdict.go{ color: #2E7D4F; }
  .verdict.ok{ color: #C9622A; }
  .verdict.no{ color: #7A1F2B; }

  .grade-row{
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .grade-badge{
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    width: 15px;
    height: 15px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #fff;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transform: translateY(1px);
  }
  .grade-a{ background: #2E7D4F; }
  .grade-b{ background: #4A7FB0; }
  .grade-c{ background: #D4A017; }
  .grade-d{ background: #C9622A; }
  .grade-f{ background: #B0392D; }

  .rule-row{
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }
  .rule-row b{ font-weight: 600; }

  .tips{
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .tips p{
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    padding-left: 12px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .tips p:last-child{ margin-bottom: 0; }
  .tips p::before{
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 7px;
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--ema50);
  }

  .footer{
    margin-top: 12px;
    padding-top: 10px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .footer .logo-img{
    height: 100px;
    width: auto;
    display: block;
  }
  .footer .pdt-logo{
    height: 100px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">

  <h1>Born Day <em>Strategy</em></h1>

  <svg class="emaline" viewBox="0 0 460 18" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <path d="M0,4 C60,14 120,2 180,10 C240,16 300,4 360,9 C400,12 430,6 460,10" stroke="#E0B400" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" opacity="0.9"/>
    <path d="M0,8 C60,15 120,6 180,12 C240,16 300,8 360,11 C400,13 430,9 460,12" stroke="#C9622A" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" opacity="0.9"/>
    <path d="M0,12 C60,16 120,10 180,14 C240,17 300,11 360,13 C400,14 430,12 460,14" stroke="#7A1F2B" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" opacity="0.9"/>
  </svg>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <div class="label">Setup Requires</div>
      <ul class="need-list">
        <li>3/5m RTH + ETH charts</li>
        <li>9-20-50 EMA overlay</li>
        <li>PDT mindset</li>
        <li>Moon Trader energy</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <div class="label">Directional Bias</div>
      <div class="bias">
        <div>★ Above 50 EMA — <span class="up">bullish</span></div>
        <div>★ Below 50 EMA — <span class="down">bearish</span></div>
        <div>9 above 20 — <span class="up">bullish</span></div>
        <div>9 below 20 — <span class="down">bearish</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="divider">

  <div class="label">EMA Spread → Trend Strength</div>
  <div class="ema-viz">
    <div class="ema-state">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 20" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <path d="M0,17 C25,12 50,5 100,1" stroke="#E0B400" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
        <path d="M0,19 C25,15 50,10 100,6" stroke="#C9622A" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
        <path d="M0,20 C25,18 50,15 100,11" stroke="#7A1F2B" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="title">Wide</div>
      <div class="sub">Strong trend, big moves</div>
      <div class="verdict go">Great to trade</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ema-state">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 20" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <path d="M0,9 C25,7 50,5 100,2" stroke="#E0B400" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
        <path d="M0,11 C25,9 50,7 100,5" stroke="#C9622A" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
        <path d="M0,13 C25,11 50,9 100,8" stroke="#7A1F2B" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="title">Narrow</div>
      <div class="sub">Weak trend, small moves</div>
      <div class="verdict ok">OK to trade</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ema-state">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 20" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <path d="M0,8 C20,14 40,4 60,12 C80,5 90,14 100,7" stroke="#E0B400" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
        <path d="M0,11 C20,5 40,14 60,7 C80,13 90,5 100,11" stroke="#C9622A" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
        <path d="M0,9 C20,12 40,6 60,10 C80,6 90,10 100,8" stroke="#7A1F2B" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="title">Tangled</div>
      <div class="sub">Chop, sideways — potential trend change</div>
      <div class="verdict no">No trade, wait</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="divider">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <div class="label">Entry</div>
      <div class="grades">
        <div class="grade-row"><span class="grade-badge grade-a">A</span> Price bounces, crosses or near 50 EMA w/clear trend or level</div>
        <div class="grade-row"><span class="grade-badge grade-b">B</span> Inside EMA's w/ 50 EMA trend</div>
        <div class="grade-row"><span class="grade-badge grade-c">C</span> Outside EMA's — potentially deeper pullback and sweeps into between 9-20-50 EMA's</div>
        <div class="grade-row"><span class="grade-badge grade-d">D</span> Inside or near tangled EMA w/o clear space being made from tangled to narrow to wide EMA's</div>
        <div class="grade-row"><span class="grade-badge grade-f">F</span> Betting against a 50 EMA trend w/o reversal indicator</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <div class="label">Be Aware</div>
      <div class="tips">
        <p>50 EMA on RTH/ETH is most important — at market open the 9-20 EMA are least effective but can be on RTH at open</p>
        <p>Watch 50 EMA and 9 EMA on the 5m chart for macro trends</p>
        <p>Watch RTH gap — can also be potential levels of support/resistance</p>
        <p>Trend flip potential when 9-20 EMA is crossing near or EMA's crosses the 50 EMA</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <img class="logo-img pdt-logo" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="PDT Trades logo">
    
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Moon Trader" class="logo-img">
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
